install all dependencies using:
    npm install

On linux, the "build:backend" script should be:
    "rm -rf; tsc; cp -R src/backend/views dist/backend/views"

On windows/cmd.exe, install the following and use this "build:backend" script:
    npm install --save-dev rimraf cpx
    "rimraf dist && tsc && cpx \"src/backend/views/**/*\" dist/views"